Step 2 : Style with CSS 
/* static/css/style.css */
footer {
    background: #333;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 0;
}

footer a {
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
}

footer a:hover {
    text-deoration: underline;
}

footer .hours {
    margin-top: 15px;
}

Result:::::
Opening Hours:
Mon - Fri: 10:00 AM - 10:00 PM
Sat - Sun: 9:00 AM - 11:00 PM
